Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.36,0:00:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I can't do it." "It's too frustrating."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Break down those hurdles.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing I can't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is being manipulated on the field?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not frightened yet I get told to go away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The path to the unseen future...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not be able to choose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes, and shuffle your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely, just like cards
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.28,0:01:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As promised, yes! you are the winner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never lose! Shuffle your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,definitely, just like cards
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.75,0:01:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that miracle...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.55,0:01:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diamond Blade!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My only Monster in enemy territory was beaten...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.48,0:01:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My opponent has four Monsters at his disposal...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.32,0:01:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I only have three Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Miracle Dimension:\N Summon the Black Magician"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dice Roll!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I move Duker of Twin Swords closer to enemy territory!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:02:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's {\i1}my{\i0} turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.89,0:02:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't make it in time, Yugi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.89,0:02:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cuz I'll make it {\i1}before{\i0} you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dice Roll!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Orgoth advances!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Orgoth is moving towards the Warp Hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.49,0:02:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking two Warp Route right onto your home turf!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm charging right in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Orgoth!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Warp!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't do something, God Orgoth will get to my Life!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dice Roll!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of my Monsters stand guard in front of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Golem, Gorogon! Move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little Wizard, move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duker of Twin Swords, move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wall of Monsters can stop God Orgoth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's {\i1}my{\i0} turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Orgoth, move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Orgoth's Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using a Magic Crest, I can raise his Attack by 10!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His Attack goes up to 40!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Orgoth, attack Iron Golem Gorogon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diamond Blade!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at least you've made it {\i1}this{\i0} far, Yugi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:03:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool~!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.25,0:04:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Go! Otogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That damn Otogi just took the lead again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, he's running out of Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think he can Summon something else, Anzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got no room left on the field to Dimension the dice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to show off your true power as a {\i1}Duelist{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-kun, you've only got two Monsters left now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you can no longer Summon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've sure tried hard since the game started.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}praise{\i0} you for that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, a cheap Duelist who cheated Pegasus stands no chance against {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did {\i1}not{\i0} cheat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dice Roll!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget the Mage's power already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little Wizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can attack Monsters from two spaces away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little Wizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning Rod!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use a Defense Crest to increase his Defense against Magic Attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Orgoth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate your Defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little Wizard's attack was deflected!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Orgoth takes 10 points of damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So his Hit Points drop to 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But God Orgoth's Attack is {\i1}40{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little Wizard takes 20 points of damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he still has 20 Hit Points left!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can still fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How naive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's my turn again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dice Roll!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Orgoth advances forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Orgoth has 40 Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And with its Special Ability,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:06:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,using Magic Crests, his Attack will increase by 30 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Orgoth's Attack Points went from 40 to {\i1}70{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if he uses his Defense Crests, I can't touch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Orgoth attacks Little Wizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super Diamond Blade!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I only have one Monster left...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no way of stopping the enemy's attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You no longer have any way to turn the tables.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If this keeps up, the game will be completely in his control.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the Duel Monsters title me and my other self won will be taken away as well...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna surrender, Yugi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, pick up the dice! I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still{\i0} talking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lousy {\i1}dog{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cheeky!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let me say this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry, Jounouchi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I went and promised I'd get your freedom back...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not fighting for {\i1}me{\i0} anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for the hundreds of Duelists out there, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the Duelists...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For all the people who fought against you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with all they had, and put their strong feelings on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same goes for that Pegasus as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He gave his all when he fought against you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he {\i1}lost{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he was the {\i1}king{\i0} of Duel Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the game's different,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you have a responsibility to give it your all,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and fight on until the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always fight until the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi! Well said!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although that ridiculous looking outfit kinda ruined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Jounouchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came pretty close to losing my sight as a Duelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if card and dice are different from each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a game's still a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll channel my thoughts in these dice,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and roll on until the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll protect my throne as the King of Duelists!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Nicely put, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my grandson for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dice Roll!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rice Roll!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use a Movement Crest to move Duker of Twin Swords ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also, with the Attack Crests I just rolled,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can attack your Monster with his Renzoku attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Otogi just used a Defense Crest...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I use all of my saved Crests, I can beat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duker of Twin Swords!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using the remainder of my Attack Crests as the cost,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use his Renzoku attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll attack God Orgoth six times!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twin Swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six Renzoku Giri!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Yaranzo's Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I change my two Trap Crests into Defense Crests!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He stopped all six of Duker of Twin Swords' Six Rengoku Giri attacks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaranzo can change any Crest in my Crest Pool
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,into any Crest I want them to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even need the unstoppable God Orgoth to put you in your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dice Roll!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Orgoth!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack the Duker of Twin Swords!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The God Orgoth's Attack Points are too high!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I raise his Defense, it won't help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diamond Blade!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Yugi!\N -Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've wiped out the Duker of Twin Swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Monsters are all wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what'll you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not have any Monsters, but I still have two of my Life left!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give this game up until the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He doesn't even have any room left to Dimension his dice...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His chances of Summoning a Monster are slim to none.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even so, his heart hasn't shaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't believe he has such a strong heart...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's got to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's got to be a way out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't any way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up hope and fall to my feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I move God Orgoth forward yet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Towards the Dungeon Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Orgoth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Dungeon Master Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't beat God Orgoth next turn, you're gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll compliment you for getting God Orgoth's Attack Points down to 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This fight's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to Summon a Monster strong enough to beat God Orgoth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}still{\i0} won't give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And just {\i1}where{\i0} do you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you're gonna {\i1}Summon{\i0} that Monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.21,0:12:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Go! Otogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:13:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-O-V-E, OTOGI!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Millions of gaming fans around the {\i1}world{\i0} are watching this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How bout you stop with the tough guy act and accept your loss like a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll {\b0}win{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll show you a {\b0}miracle{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And for all the Duelists in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dice Roll!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no place to Dimension the dice on this field!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so sure of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otogi, there are {\i1}various{\i0} places left to Dimension the dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can figure that out without {\i1}you{\i0} telling me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then allow me to {\i1}show{\i0} you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dimension Dice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, {\i1}shit{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Dimension...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon the Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Magician...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It {\i1}can't{\i0} be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Otogi boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I would like to make a small change to this game upon its publication.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I assume that is okay with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But what {\b0}kind{\b1} of change?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I would like to link it with some of the Monsters from Duel Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I would like to add a new Monster with its own Effect
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to Dungeon Monsters, truly making it the perfect game!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A new Monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is a secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You shall find out through playing the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had no idea the Black Magician was added to my version of the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the hell is the Special Effect of this Monster Pegasus was talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If it has the same Effects as in Duel Monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:14:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm seriously screwed here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since I was trying to beat an enemy familiar with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}maybe I should have done more research on his Monsters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I made a huge mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then move Black Magician forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I attack God Orgoth with the Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Yes! \N-Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He beat Otogi's best Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Yes! Nice one! Get 'im, Yugi!\N -No~! Otogi-kun got beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In that case, I'll use my remaining Crests to finish this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I left my trump for that sole purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dice Roll!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Assassin, move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now it's time to open the eagerly-awaited treasure chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can look forward to rest later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's now {\b0}your{\b1} turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Rare Item...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monster Cannon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monster Cannon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Monster Cannon is one of the Rare Items
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that uses Monsters as ammo to destroy the enemy's Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And its target is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Black Magician!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monster Cannon! Activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate your Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Silk Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.72,0:17:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the Black Magician hiding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monster Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I get him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By activating the one-time use Magical Silk Hats using a Trap Crest,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he can evade the enemy's attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaranzo! Pull back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm certain this isn't the Black Magician's only Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to protect myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dice Roll!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:18:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use two Magic Crests to activate Black Magician's second Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Death Box!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the Special Ability Pegasus mentioned?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaranzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Monsters were wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.68,0:18:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dream's gone for good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I created that game all by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.43,0:19:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For my dream of making Dungeon Dice Monsters famous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.85,0:19:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if that dream's gone, I have nothing left!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dungeon Dice Monsters is an awesome game!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm-hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're truly amazing competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could be in for some real problems if I'm not careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Duel Monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dungeon Dice Monsters is sure to be accepted by everyone around the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You really think that's possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like {\i1}you{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I like this {\i1}game{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach me how to play too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So just like you promised, you have to set Jounouchi-kun free.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll be continuing to play Duel Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, of course, Yugi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry I put Jounouchi-kun through all of that hardship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm over it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who the opponent you face in a game is,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they shouldn't be played to get revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a great game should be used to make friends with everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I can become {\i1}your{\i0} friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from Industrial Illusions INC!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They want to contract Dungeon Dice Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-You did it, Otogi!\N -Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad for you, Otogi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:21:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Yugi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I put you through so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just forget about all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way someone with a strong heart like you would have cheated against Pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not strong all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart's strong because of the many friends I made...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and my wonderful partner as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.97,0:21:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(137,145)}"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi's Millennium Puzzle was stolen by a suspicious man wearing a cloak!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.73,0:21:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi vows to believe in his other self, and that he'll definitely get it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.03,0:21:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi finally finds where the Puzzle is,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but winds up in a Duel against the cloaked man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what's he after?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Challenge From the Past: The terrifying Zera"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.91,0:21:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've been here, been in this place before
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the classroom shaded by the setting sun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.07,0:22:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I laughed along and pointed with my too shortly cut bangs
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.17,0:22:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little by little, time keeps going
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.47,0:22:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bangs now over my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.64,0:22:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sunset took everyone together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.85,0:23:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure nothing changed while we were there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.11,0:23:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.28,0:23:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept on searching for something
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.45,0:23:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you understood such a senseless time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.62,0:23:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the answer
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.34,0:23:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From here, always...
